<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>I'm Sorry, My Love</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            flex-direction: column;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        h1 {
            color: #d63384;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        p {
            color: #444;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .heart {
            color: red;
            font-size: 40px;
            animation: heartbeat 1s infinite alternate;
        }
        @keyframes heartbeat {
            from { transform: scale(1); }
            to { transform: scale(1.3); }
        }
        .btn {
            background: #ff4d6d;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #e63950;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        .floating-hearts {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .floating-hearts span {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: red;
            opacity: 0.7;
            animation: floatUp 5s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes floatUp {
            from { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.7; }
            to { transform: translateY(-100px); opacity: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="floating-hearts">
        <span>❤</span><span>❤</span><span>❤</span><span>❤</span>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>namaig uuchlaarai  <span class="heart">❤</span></h1>
        <p>Odoo yuc bolson chinii ugend orj chinii tald l baih bolno shuu, bi chamd etsest butsaltgui hairtai shuu. 
            Yuc bolson bi aldaaga zasnaa hrn bugdiig ni heleed ugchihuj baigaarai bi zarimiig ni uuruc mededgui baih.
            Bi cmg ndtai haritsah durguu baigan bh l gej bodsiin angid yuuc yrihgu yriy ghler durgu bgam shg hariulad bsn bolhoor chine,
            bas hajuud cn ywiy ghler albaar holdood baigam shg. 
            (Bi shamd uneheer ih hairtaig bitgii martaarai)

        </p>
        <button class="btn" onclick="alert('Hairtai shuu! ❤')">Uuchlaarai</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
